Project Name
This project is a full-stack web application built with a React frontend and an Express backend. The frontend is developed using Vite and Tailwind CSS, while the backend uses TypeScript, Express, and various middleware for authentication, file uploads, and logging. The application is designed to [briefly describe the project's purpose or functionality, e.g., "manage user data with secure authentication and a responsive UI"].
